### Cole este arquivo na extens√£o REST Client (VS Code) ou use curl/Postman.

@base = http://localhost:4000
@token = 1234567890
@json = application/json

### Listar tarefas
GET {{base}}/tarefas
x-api-token: {{token}}

### Obter 1 tarefa
GET {{base}}/tarefas/1
x-api-token: {{token}}

### Criar tarefa
POST {{base}}/tarefas
Content-Type: {{json}}
x-api-token: {{token}}

{
  "tarefa": "Estudar Node",
  "descricao": "CRUD simples",
  "responsavel": "Vanderlei"
}

### Atualizar tarefa
PUT {{base}}/tarefas/1
Content-Type: {{json}}
x-api-token: {{token}}

{
  "tarefa": "Estudar Node (atualizado)",
  "descricao": "CRUD simples e token",
  "responsavel": "Vanderlei"
}

### Excluir tarefa
DELETE {{base}}/tarefas/1
x-api-token: {{token}}